spec_data.Name: python3-keycloak-httpd-client-install
spec_data.Description:
Keycloak is an authentication server. This package contains libraries and
programs which can invoke the Keycloak REST API and configure clients
of a Keycloak server.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 26 Jul 2017 08:26:56 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Tools to configure Apache HTTPD as Keycloak client
